  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.3SalesService\nOn this page\nThis app is available in Sales and Creatio Service products. For other products, the application must be purchased separately from the Marketplace.\nUse the **Knowledge Management** app to create and maintain an electronic library of helpful materials that the employees use daily. Enrich the knowledge base with internal company policies, answers to the frequently asked questions, equipment specs, and other valuable information.\nFig. 1 Knowledge base article\n![Fig.\u00a01 Knowledge base article](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/images/Composable_apps/Knowledge_Management/knowledge_management_overview/scr_knowledge_base_article.png)\nYou can set up different access levels for the items in the knowledge base and their relations. This ensures the answers are easy to find in the knowledge base for everyone, including your employees from different departments, partners, and customers.\n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[Create a knowledge base article](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1006)",
